1
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:34,630
Since when did the descendants of the heroes who guarded the Imperial Pass

2
00:00:34,800 --> 00:00:36,730
become slaves

3
00:00:36,730 --> 00:00:38,860
that you ants can trample at will?

4
00:00:38,930 --> 00:00:40,700
Spare me, senior!

5
00:00:46,530 --> 00:00:47,360
Are they

6
00:00:47,800 --> 00:00:51,600
the immortal brother and sister?

7
00:00:53,160 --> 00:00:55,760
The sinners of the Luo family pay our respects.

8
00:00:58,130 --> 00:01:00,360
Who dares to cause trouble here?

9
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:04,800
You have a death wish.

10
00:01:08,700 --> 00:01:10,100
The immortals have descended.

11
00:01:10,100 --> 00:01:12,060
Please save us.

12
00:01:12,500 --> 00:01:13,100
Lord Gu Di.

13
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:13,860
These

14
00:01:14,100 --> 00:01:16,560
sinners were exiled by the Ancestral Court.

15
00:01:16,700 --> 00:01:18,960
The Luo clan colluded with foreign enemies

16
00:01:18,960 --> 00:01:20,130
and the demon race.

17
00:01:20,260 --> 00:01:22,730
They have long been stripped of their ancestors' glory

18
00:01:22,730 --> 00:01:24,590
and are sinners of our human race.

19
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:28,600
I hope you won't interfere in the affairs of the Ancestral Court.

20
00:01:29,700 --> 00:01:32,460
If Her Majesty the Empress blames us,

21
00:01:33,060 --> 00:01:34,930
even if you are a quasi-emperor,

22
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:36,660
I'm afraid

23
00:01:37,130 --> 00:01:38,729
you'll be held accountable.

24
00:01:41,330 --> 00:01:42,100
Are you

25
00:01:42,700 --> 00:01:45,430
trying to use the Ancestral Court to pressure me?

26
00:01:45,830 --> 00:01:46,600
I wouldn't dare.

27
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:49,660
This is just Her Majesty's personal edict,

28
00:01:50,729 --> 00:01:52,560
to strip the Luo clan of their status

29
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,960
and demote them to criminal bloodlines.

30
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:55,660
What a bullshit empress.

31
00:01:55,759 --> 00:01:57,460
Your six ancient clans may acknowledge her,

32
00:01:57,460 --> 00:01:59,030
but my Gu family doesn't.

33
00:01:59,160 --> 00:02:01,300
Even if Jiang Yun herself were here,

34
00:02:01,900 --> 00:02:03,500
she wouldn't dare to stop me.

35
00:02:03,860 --> 00:02:05,260
I'll give you three breaths

36
00:02:05,260 --> 00:02:07,100
to disappear from my sight.

37
00:02:07,530 --> 00:02:08,259
Three.

38
00:02:16,060 --> 00:02:17,900
This Old Demon Gu is too fierce.

39
00:02:18,100 --> 00:02:20,530
I can't do anything against a quasi-emperor.

40
00:02:20,530 --> 00:02:21,600
I'm just working for someone else.

41
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:23,000
Why should I risk my life?

42
00:02:25,660 --> 00:02:28,329
Thank you for saving us, immortals.

43
00:02:28,660 --> 00:02:30,900
Thank you, immortals.

44
00:02:30,930 --> 00:02:32,400
I just received a message from the Sinners' Village.

45
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:34,460
That old demon Gu Linyuan went there.

46
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:37,200
It seems he wants to cause trouble for us.

47
00:02:38,230 --> 00:02:40,460
That Old Demon Gu is going too far.

48
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:42,960
Instead of staying in his Gu family in the Eastern Wasteland,

49
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,560
he must want to blackmail us.

50
00:02:44,660 --> 00:02:46,360
We can't let him succeed.

51
00:02:46,500 --> 00:02:48,200
Granny Jinhua is absolutely right.

52
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,530
This demon is arrogant and domineering.

53
00:02:49,530 --> 00:02:51,960
Why don't you, Granny Jinhua, handle this personally

54
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,130
to go and stop that old demon?

55
00:02:53,130 --> 00:02:54,760
We are willing to assist you from the sidelines.

56
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:56,100
You grown men,

57
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:58,329
do you have any sense of responsibility?

58
00:02:58,329 --> 00:03:01,430
You only know how to bully an old lady like me.

59
00:03:01,430 --> 00:03:02,400
You have thick skin

60
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:03,360
and deep cultivation.

61
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:05,700
Yet you want me to be on the front lines?

62
00:03:05,900 --> 00:03:08,530
Who doesn't know that Gu Linyuan is fierce and cruel?

63
00:03:08,530 --> 00:03:09,760
He kills without blinking.

64
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,600
Sigh.

65
00:03:11,230 --> 00:03:14,360
Then let Elder Wang go and stop that old demon.

66
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,160
I

67
00:03:15,930 --> 00:03:18,230
just finished my seclusion and broke through to the Saint Realm.

68
00:03:18,230 --> 00:03:19,760
Now you want me to go and stop

69
00:03:19,760 --> 00:03:22,000
a quasi-emperor holding an Ultimate Imperial Weapon?

70
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,329
The Luo clan's affairs

71
00:03:23,430 --> 00:03:25,890
have nothing to do with my Han family anyway.

72
00:03:26,030 --> 00:03:27,700
I'm just here for the show.

73
00:03:27,700 --> 00:03:31,000
That demon Gu Linyuan is going after the Luo clan remnants.

74
00:03:31,100 --> 00:03:32,930
What happened to the Luo clan back then

75
00:03:32,930 --> 00:03:34,829
must not have any accidents.

76
00:03:34,900 --> 00:03:37,900
If worst comes to worst, I'll ask the Patriarch to come out.

77
00:03:37,900 --> 00:03:39,100
Lord Gu Di.

78
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:44,060
My Luo Clan has been wronged!

79
00:03:44,430 --> 00:03:46,260
My son was the patriarch of the Luo Clan,

80
00:03:46,260 --> 00:03:48,400
fighting to the death for the human race his whole life.

81
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,960
Yet, he was slandered by the major ancient clans,

82
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:53,760
falsely accusing us of colluding with the demons.

83
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:15,600
Before my father died, he pushed me away

84
00:04:15,860 --> 00:04:17,500
and told me to find my aunt,

85
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:20,329
so she could come back and save us.

86
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:21,399
But...

87
00:04:22,029 --> 00:04:25,600
Ling'er has no idea where Aunt is.

88
00:04:26,960 --> 00:04:28,060
Your foolish aunt

89
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:30,100
is still at the Imperial Pass frontline,

90
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:31,960
shedding blood for those hypocrites

91
00:04:31,960 --> 00:04:33,620
in the Human Ancestral Court.

92
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:36,560
Her last blood relatives are about to be wiped out,

93
00:04:37,060 --> 00:04:39,720
and she is still completely unaware like a fool.

94
00:04:40,230 --> 00:04:43,060
In my past life, I only knew there was a turmoil in the Human Ancestral Court.

95
00:04:43,060 --> 00:04:44,730
The Imperial Pass was almost lost,

96
00:04:44,730 --> 00:04:47,230
and thanks to the enduring providence of the human race, the demons were repelled.

97
00:04:47,230 --> 00:04:48,560
Little did I know that behind all this,

98
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:50,100
there lay such a deep-seated blood feud.

99
00:04:50,100 --> 00:04:51,000
I didn't expect

100
00:04:51,300 --> 00:04:53,730
the Ancestral Court, the origin of the human race,

101
00:04:53,730 --> 00:04:55,930
to secretly harbor such filthy,

102
00:04:56,130 --> 00:04:57,500
heinous deeds.

103
00:04:58,460 --> 00:04:59,900
Exploiting meritorious heroes

104
00:04:59,900 --> 00:05:01,430
and slaughtering their own kind.

105
00:05:01,430 --> 00:05:02,500
As fellow humans,

106
00:05:02,760 --> 00:05:04,160
it's simply despicable.

107
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,860
Can't take it already?

108
00:05:06,300 --> 00:05:06,960
If you knew

109
00:05:06,960 --> 00:05:10,430
that Jiang Yun, the Destiny Empress chosen by the Ancestral Court,

110
00:05:10,430 --> 00:05:13,030
would later fall in love with the Demon Prince,

111
00:05:13,030 --> 00:05:15,900
abandon the frontline human generals with a single decree,

112
00:05:15,900 --> 00:05:18,030
and then secretly release the Demon Prince back to the outer realm,

113
00:05:18,030 --> 00:05:19,600
you would probably spit blood out of anger on the spot.

114
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:20,200
Tomorrow,

115
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:22,260
you will lead the rest of the Luo Clan in Sin Village

116
00:05:22,260 --> 00:05:23,390
and migrate with me.

117
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:25,030
The Human Ancestral Court cannot tolerate you.

118
00:05:25,030 --> 00:05:26,630
The territory of my Imperial Gu Clan is vast.

119
00:05:26,630 --> 00:05:27,930
Let alone a mere few thousand people,

120
00:05:27,930 --> 00:05:28,990
even ten times more

121
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:30,860
would have enough room to settle.

122
00:05:31,400 --> 00:05:32,500
Thank you, Emperor Gu.

123
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:33,700
Your great kindness,

124
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:35,659
my Luo Clan will never forget.

125
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:38,600
Everyone says Master is cruel and tyrannical,

126
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,700
killing without blinking an eye.

127
00:05:39,700 --> 00:05:41,100
But with my own eyes, I see

128
00:05:41,500 --> 00:05:42,630
he clearly distinguishes gratitude from grudges

129
00:05:42,630 --> 00:05:44,230
and values loyalty and affection.

130
00:05:44,230 --> 00:05:46,530
Compared to the hypocrites in my past life who preached morality

131
00:05:46,530 --> 00:05:48,530
but were actually vile and despicable,

132
00:05:48,530 --> 00:05:49,530
he is much better.

133
00:05:49,860 --> 00:05:50,260
[Ding]

134
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:52,730
Disciple Ji Qingchen's affection has increased again.

135
00:05:52,730 --> 00:05:54,600
Obtained 500 Destiny Providence Points.

136
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:59,130
Current Total Providence Points: 5597.
